-1 FELINE~

. {rThe Feline are a race descended from the great cats. For long years in
their past, the Feline were enslaved by wizards to serve as familiars.
 They are renowned, however, for their agility and their "nine lives". 
It is said a Feline can withstand blows in battle (or from an angry master) 
that would kill a human outright.

The thick fur of the Feline makes them resistant to cold, but also very
vulnerable to fire. They also abhor water and are liable to drown in
it. Despite heavy modification by their former masters, the Feline
retain the large claws and fangs of their ancestors. This gives them
the ability to inflict extra damage during a fight, but the claws are
not retractable so it is difficult for a Feline to walk unnoticed. The
Feline are also famed for their street fighting ability. 

Feline tend to be smaller than humans, averaging about 5' in height.
They have a very muscular builds, though, more so than would be expected. 
Fur on feline's can run from almost none to 90% of their body covered. 
Their colorings vary.{x
